✅ Java 17 – All Major Features with Examples
1. Records (Finalized)
What

Concise, immutable data-carrier classes.

Example
public record User(int id, String name) {}


Usage:

User u = new User(1, "Akanksha");
System.out.println(u.id());

Why

Removes boilerplate (constructor, getters, equals, hashCode).

2. Sealed Classes (Finalized)
What

Restrict which classes can extend a class or interface.

Example
public sealed class Shape permits Circle, Rectangle {}

final class Circle extends Shape {}
final class Rectangle extends Shape {}

Why

Controlled inheritance, better domain modeling.

3. Pattern Matching for instanceof (Finalized)
Before Java 16
if (obj instanceof String) {
    String s = (String) obj;
    System.out.println(s.length());
}

Java 17
if (obj instanceof String s) {
    System.out.println(s.length());
}

Why

Less casting, cleaner code.

4. Switch Expressions (Standard)
Old Switch
int result;
switch (day) {
    case 1: result = 10; break;
    case 2: result = 20; break;
    default: result = 0;
}

Java 17
int result = switch (day) {
    case 1 -> 10;
    case 2 -> 20;
    default -> 0;
};

Why

Expression-based, no fall-through bugs.

5. Text Blocks (""") (Standard)
Before
String json = "{\n" +
              "  \"id\": 1\n" +
              "}";

Java 17
String json = """
        {
          "id": 1
        }
        """;

Why

Readable multi-line strings (SQL, JSON, HTML).

6. Helpful NullPointerExceptions
Before
Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NullPointerException

Java 17
Cannot invoke "User.getName()" because "user" is null

Why

Much easier debugging.

7. Stream API Enhancements
toList() (Immutable)
List<Integer> list = stream.toList();


Instead of:

Collectors.toList()

8. Local Variable Type Inference (var) (Enhanced)
var name = "Akanksha";  // String
var list = List.of(1, 2, 3);


Rules:

Only for local variables

Not for method parameters or fields

9. Sealed Interfaces
public sealed interface Payment permits Card, Upi {}

record Card(String number) implements Payment {}
record Upi(String id) implements Payment {}

Why

Very common with record.

10. Pattern Matching + Sealed + Switch (Power Feature)
static double area(Shape shape) {
    return switch (shape) {
        case Circle c -> 100;
        case Rectangle r -> 200;
    };
}


✔ Compiler forces all cases handled

11. New Random Generator API
RandomGenerator rg = RandomGenerator.getDefault();
int num = rg.nextInt(100);


More flexible than java.util.Random.

12. Strong Encapsulation of JDK Internals

Illegal access to internal APIs blocked

Improves security and stability

(Interview answer: Better modularity and safety)

13. Foreign Function & Memory API (Incubator)

Allows Java to interact with native memory safely.

(Usually not asked in depth for 2–3 yrs experience)

14. Deprecations & Removals

Removed:

Applets

Security Manager (deprecated)

RMI Activation

Interview note:

Java 17 cleans legacy features.
